  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2.\u0d91\u0db8\u0dca.\u0d91\u0dc6\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0da0\u0dca\u0da1\u0dcf \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dcf\u0da2\u0dba\u0dad\u0dca \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d85\u0dad \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Looking at the IMF negotiations, the Paris Club also lends a helping hand to Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "\"Paris Club Members\" have stated in a statement that they are ready to start the debt relief process for Sri Lanka.",
        "The statement reiterates its willingness to coordinate with non-Paris Club official bilateral creditors to provide the necessary financial assurances and provide the necessary financial assurances in a timely manner while the Paris Club prepares to initiate a debt resolution procedure.",
        "The Paris Club has accepted the official level agreement between the Government of Sri Lanka and officials of the International Monetary Fund for a 48-month plan under extended credit facilities.",
        "The agreement contains important measures to maintain macroeconomic stability and public debt sustainability.",
        "They have also confirmed their ability to deal fairly with other official bilateral creditors as already suggested."
      ],
